original_title: WWE In Your House 8: Beware of Dog
overview: In Your House: Beware of Dog features Shawn Michaels vs. "The British Bulldog" Davey Boy Smith for the WWE Championship; Goldust vs. The Undertaker for the WWWE Intercontinental Title; Stone Cold Steve Austin vs Savio Vega and more!
title: WWE In Your House 8: Beware of Dog
